/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/swapp_staking_findonly_1round_clean/foundry_validation/F-001_Unchecked_Compound_error_codes_desynchro/codex_stderr_attempt0.log:30:- impact: If a Compound market is paused, illiquid, or otherwise returns a non-zero code, the contract's internal principal accounting diverges from its real Compound position. Stablecoin deposits can be credited without being invested, withdrawals can succeed only while idle cash exists and then start reverting for later users, and interest-harvest flows operate on stale assumptions. This creates pool-wide withdrawal denial and unfair first-exit behavior for stablecoin depositors.
